data.text:
Sibley, IA

Delia Thompson age 70 formerly of Fulda, MN died Saturday, June 15, 2024, at Sibley Specialty Care in Sibley, IA.

Delia Ann Thompson was born on October 15, 1953, in Slayton, MN, the daughter of William and Ann (Schelhaas) Overman.

Delia enjoyed cleaning houses and worked at a nursing home in Fulda, MN. She also worked with hospice in Slayton, MN.

Delia is survived by her four children, Mark Lidtke (Jodi Steveson-Lidtke) of Sibley, IA, Jackie (Frank) Skaggs of White Oak, TX, Jessica (Justin) Gaarder of Worthington, MN, and Alvin Thompson of Fulda, MN; six grandchildren, Hunter, Dominc, Hoyt, Zachery, Mickenzie, and Harrison; two brothers and two sisters.

She was preceded in death by her parents William and Ann Overman.

Memorials can be sent to the family at: 915 6th Avenue, Sibley, Iowa 51249.
